@startuml
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
left to right direction

rectangle "Phase 1\nRelease Hardening" as P1 {
  note as P1N
  - Qt client/server system tests
  - package/install direction
  - migration discipline
  - health and backup basics
  end note
}

rectangle "Phase 2\nOwnership + Stock Truth" as P2 {
  note as P2N
  - Company
  - StorageLocation
  - stock ledger
  - generic catalog attributes
  end note
}

rectangle "Phase 3\nProcurement Completion" as P3 {
  note as P3N
  - incoming invoices
  - attachments
  - preview/validate/commit
  - background jobs
  end note
}

rectangle "Phase 4\nSales Fulfillment" as P4 {
  note as P4N
  - reservation/posting policy
  - rendered invoice outputs
  - stronger audit trail
  end note
}

rectangle "Phase 5\nPlatform Extension" as P5 {
  note as P5N
  - analytics depth
  - integrations
  - installer polish
  - autoparts domain pack
  end note
}

P1 --> P2
P2 --> P3
P2 --> P4
P3 --> P4
P4 --> P5

note bottom of P2
Do not add multi-company behavior before
ownership and storage rules are explicit.
end note

note bottom of P3
Do not automate invoices or labels before
product identity and stock truth are stable.
end note
@enduml
